<br>
the _main_ thing I enjoy about a druid is being able to gate myself around to where I adventure.  I like other things, but, to be honest, that was the difference between EQ being enjoyable for me, and a royal PITA.  For what it's worth I leveled a ranger a good was then quit because I hated having to run all over creation.<br>
<br>
so, great, now we are back to having to run around within our new home continent.  whoopdefrigin do.  Who knows, maybe it will turn out that I am incorrect about this, or maybe it will change, but IMO, this is a huge blow to the overall gameplay of being a druid.<br>
