</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uaurigastarlighter.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Auriga Starlighter</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(12/4/01 2:51:30 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Looks like our porting days might be over...</span><hr size=1> I'll add my 2 cents to Sweetie's above. I love just being able to port myself around. If I take others with me or can earn some cash that way then great but primarily I'm a druid because *I* like it. If I wanted to make silly money I'd PL a chanter and stick him at the entrance of Velketor's.<br>
<br>
